snippet.title: ✅  Johnny Depp's ex-wife Amber Heard paid secret midnight visits by Elon Musk
snippet.description:
💖 Please Visit: https://www.facebook.com/Scathc/
💖 Please Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQju4Bo1Tjk9SzhHQDknWaw?sub_confirmation=1
✍   A concierge working at the building where  lived with Amber Heard has claimed she was regularly paid secret late-night visits by Elon Musk.   Alejandro Romero, who worked at the apartment building where Depp shared a penthouse with Heard, gave evidence at London's High Court today via videolink from Beverly Hills.  He said SpaceX billionaire Musk visited Heard "regularly late at night from 11pm to midnight" while Depp "was not at home".  "I believe he visited a few times a week," he said.  Mr Romero said the visits began in 2015 around the time Depp injured his hand while filming Pirates of the Caribbean.   He said he remembered the date because his musician pal, who was a huge fan of Depp, was worried the finger injury the actor suffered would have meant he could not play the guitar.  "The same day I saw Mr Musk," he added.  Mr Romero said in his witness statement: "My interaction with Ms Heard was limited to brief interactions about logistical matters with the apartments, including ...
💖 #JohnnyDepp, #AmberHeard, #ElonMusk, #CaraDelevingne
